
Overview of noun convoy

The noun convoy has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (1) convoy -- (a procession of land vehicles traveling together)
2. convoy -- (a collection of merchant ships with an escort of warships)
3. convoy -- (the act of escorting while in transit)

